text: David Forde (born 5 July 1976 in Ogonnelloe, County Clare) is an Irish sportsperson. He plays hurling with his local club Ogonnelloe and was a member of the Clare senior inter-county team in the 1990s and 2000s. He played as a forward. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Ogonnelloe hurlers Category:Clare inter-county hurlers
